Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.979 --> 00:00:06.440
 Fresh vegetables, fruits and berries all year round - this is possible 

00:00:06.440 --> 00:00:08.009
 with modern freezers. 

00:00:08.009 --> 00:00:12.820
 Freestanding vertical freezers INDESIT SFR - roomy 

00:00:12.820 --> 00:00:15.179
 and convenient devices with an attractive price 

00:00:15.179 --> 00:00:23.910
 and thoughtful organization of internal space. 

00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:27.089
 Freezers are represented by three models: low 

00:00:27.089 --> 00:00:31.800
 SFR 100, taller SFR 167 in white or silver 

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:36.300
 and SFR 167 NF with the No Frost defrost system. 

00:00:36.300 --> 00:00:40.070
 With design everything is clear - it is modern and ergonomic. 

00:00:40.070 --> 00:00:44.010
 What is hidden inside the freezers? 

00:00:44.010 --> 00:00:46.800
 Note the division of the internal space into compartments 

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:49.469
 for freezing and compartments for food storage. 

00:00:49.469 --> 00:00:54.239
 The SFR 167 NF has ice containers. 

00:00:54.239 --> 00:00:57.030
 Offices for freezing have a hinged lid. 

00:00:57.030 --> 00:01:00.850
 The bottom here are of two types: perforated surface - perfect 

00:01:00.850 --> 00:01:03.360
 suitable for freezing small berries, dumplings 

00:01:03.360 --> 00:01:06.540
 or dumplings, and the lattice - on it can be evenly 

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:09.360
 distribute for freezing pieces of meat, fish and others 

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:10.750
 larger products. 

00:01:10.750 --> 00:01:13.770
 These compartments are suitable for both freezing and storage. 

00:01:13.770 --> 00:01:14.770
 products. 

00:01:14.770 --> 00:01:17.370
 But for long-term storage, retractable 

00:01:17.370 --> 00:01:18.370
 the boxes. 

00:01:18.370 --> 00:01:21.110
 When foods are frozen, you can move them to 

00:01:21.110 --> 00:01:22.110
 these compartments. 

00:01:22.110 --> 00:01:25.700
 The boxes are large enough, they can fit in banks 

00:01:25.700 --> 00:01:26.890
 and big bottles. 

00:01:26.890 --> 00:01:30.170
 By the way, on the freezer door there is a table showing 

00:01:30.170 --> 00:01:32.690
 what is the maximum time recommended to store 

00:01:32.690 --> 00:01:35.100
 this or that product. 

00:01:35.100 --> 00:01:37.450
 The temperature is regulated by a handle. 

00:01:37.450 --> 00:01:40.030
 All freezers have the function of fast freezing, 

00:01:40.030 --> 00:01:42.810
 which lowers the temperature to a minimum for short 

00:01:42.810 --> 00:01:45.390
 time intervals, so freezing 

00:01:45.390 --> 00:01:48.850
 faster, and their useful properties are not lost. 

00:01:48.850 --> 00:01:53.460
 Fast freezing is turned on and off manually. 

00:01:53.460 --> 00:02:00.100
 Freezers SFR 100 and 167 need to defrost manually, SFR 167 NF is equipped 

00:02:00.100 --> 00:02:01.560
 system no frost. 

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:04.030
 Note that this defrosting system does not allow 

00:02:04.030 --> 00:02:06.880
 products stick together in one ice ball, and 

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:09.140
 they are easily separated from each other. 

00:02:09.140 --> 00:02:12.719
 In general, INDESIT SFR freezers are simple and affordable. 

00:02:12.719 --> 00:02:13.890
 option for home. 

00:02:13.890 --> 00:02:16.569
 They provide everything you need for daily 

00:02:16.569 --> 00:02:18.719
 use, and this is the most important thing. 

